{"type": "article", "id": 49862, "title": "刘德华给支付宝拍广告，星巴克发布 26 张城市星礼卡 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-02-02T04:24:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 47266, "name": "狗年"}, {"id": 2399, "name": "支付宝"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 30, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/201802021202217RK6BsuUCGDmdQz3.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://socialbeta.com/t/jiafangyifang-news-20180201\" rel=\"nofollow\">支付宝找刘德华合作了一首 2018 年版的《恭喜发财五福来》</a></b>，目前已经在虾米音乐上线。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0542khqfk1&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/43211.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">星巴克发布 26 张 2018 城市星礼卡，包含 1 张中国卡和 25 张城市卡</a></b>。自从 2015 年首次推出城市系列星享卡以来，星巴克至今一共推出过 2 次城市系列星享卡。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202115047XPprEziCmIVuS4o3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695652\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25574.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫为一众老字号品牌发布了 GIF 海报，</b></a>同仁堂、美心、知味观、广州酒家、乔家栅……看起来年味挺足。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802021152522VXOJfnq8Cz9Lbw5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.643750\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202115337E2nFQBjX7dGSyzew.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25671.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LV 也发布了一组狗年表情包</b></a>，另外在产品设计上也把柴犬作为重要的形象元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202115529KOTdLknPHjv6MQcr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202115625tV7MZAJ6oYiUEahv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202115657g0EJ27RBDcuMV8tf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.843800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180202115705R7jiqXAblv05Q6HL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774557\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/creativity/subarus-doggie-drivers-are-back-and-just-rollin-along-in-new-ads/\" rel=\"nofollow\">斯巴鲁重启了 #DOG Tested ，DOG Approved#营销</a></b>，发布了三支狗狗开斯巴鲁的广告。从 2009 年开始，宠物就开始频繁出现在斯巴鲁广告中。<br></p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o0540q7siqk&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b>为呼吁拯救受少子化影响而员工流失的日本中小企业，日本中小企业机构做了个广告《社畜博物馆》</b>，用雕塑的方式展示了种种上班族的痛苦面容——连休结束、无法接受现实、站在玄关绝望的上班族；面对深夜客户不止的电话，发出悲鸣的年轻社员……非常形象了。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=r0541w6fwjy&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-3-43374.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>北京电通赢得华为比稿</b></a>。通过与 MKTG 伦敦、The Story Lab 上海的合作，北京电通将负责华为公司全球内容营销业务。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：支付宝</p>"}